Package jetbrains.mps.workbench.choose

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ElementPresentation<T>
    This is what chooser model needs to know about list elements to represent them in the UI.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChooseByNameData<T>
    Data model for a chooser that picks elements by name.
    ElementDescriptor
    Bridge between element in chooser list element and its UI presentation.
    LanguagesPresentation
    Knows how to represent deployed languages for ChooseByNameData
    ModelScopeIterable
    Gives access to scope's models as iterable collection of SModelReference, to use in ChooseByNameData.setScope(Iterable, Iterable).
    ModelsPresentation
    Knows how to represent models for ChooseByNameData
    ModuleScopeIterable
    Gives access to scope's modules as iterable collection of SModuleReference, to use in ChooseByNameData.setScope(Iterable, Iterable).
    ModulesPresentation
    Knows how to represent modules for ChooseByNameData
    NavigationTargetPresentation
    Tells ChooseByNameData how to render NavigationParticipant.NavigationTarget
    NavigationTargetScopeIterable
    Serves as a SearchScope-backed source of NavigationParticipant.NavigationTarget for ChooseByNameData
    NodePointerNavigationItem
    Wrap a node reference as NavigationItem, to inject into IDEA's services that demand NavigationItem or ItemPresentation, like Go To.
    NodesPresentation
    Tells ChooseByNameData how to represent nodes
